Ubslim is a bash script to install slimmed Ubuntu LTS 24.04.01.

Fully netinstall.
No snap.
No sudo.
No gpt.
No network-manager.
Just base system + kernel + xorg + fluxbox.

Usage:
  Boot from any LiveCD distro, then
# wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/vallbsd/ubslim/refs/heads/main/ubslim.sh
# bash ubslim.sh

